poetry-shir-entire-tribe\/","url_meta":{"origin":6358,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Satire: Worst liar attacks entire tribe in poetry","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 22, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the greatest liar among people is a man who insults another man by satirizing the entire tribe, and a man who disowns his father and accuses his mother of adultery.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 3761 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35529,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/04\/dua-amr-bil-maruf\/","url_meta":{"origin":6358,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Supplication not answered unless enjoining good","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 4, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cEnjoin good and forbid evil before you call upon Allah and He does not answer you.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 4004 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35732,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/21\/water-after-toilet\/","url_meta":{"origin":6358,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Cleanliness: The Prophet always uses water after call of nature","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 21, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: I never saw the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, come out from the toilet but that he cleansed with water. Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 354 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0631\u064e\u0623\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u062e\u064e\u0631\u064e\u062c\u064e \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17429,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/01\/prophet-sleeps-after-isha\/","url_meta":{"origin":6358,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Isha: The Prophet sleeps after evening prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 1, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would not sleep before evening prayer\u00a0and he would not stay up after it. Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 702 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0646\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0628\u0652\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0627\u0621\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0627\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17576,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/14\/forgive-aisha-all-sins\/","url_meta":{"origin":6358,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Forgiveness: O Allah, forgive Aisha for all her sins","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 14, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: When I saw the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, with a cheerful face, I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, supplicate to Allah for me.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cO Allah, forgive Aisha for her past and future sins, in secret and in public.\u201d Aisha laughed so much\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34708,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/21\/dua-good-qadr\/","url_meta":{"origin":6358,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Qadr: I ask for Your every decree to be good","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"D